Conduct toolbox talks, SHE inductions, and training sessions focused on electrical safety.
Carry out site inspections, identify unsafe acts/conditions, and recommend corrective actions.
Ensure implementation of Lockout-Tagout (LOTO), Permit-to-Work (PTW) system, and other electrical safety measures.
Lead accident/incident investigations related to electrical works, prepare reports, and ensure preventive measures.
Liaise with client representatives, statutory bodies, and internal stakeholders on electrical SHE compliance.
Support the preparation of SHE performance reports, audits, and management reviews.
Promote awareness of safe practices, sustainability, and environmental protection among the workforce.
Ensuring of Electrical safety at site, Routine inspection of electrical installation, check all electrical installation as per electrical slandered, Earthing, elcb checking as per check list and maintain records
