Conduct training and skill development of team members as per requirements
Ensure availability of all critical spares and cost-effectively manage spares.
Manage all planned and reactive maintenance of non-plant areas attached to CES workshop plant areas.
Support / Implement MOCs and CAPEXs flawlessly.
Implement life cycle plan / 5 year Obsolescence plan.
Ensure compliance with all PM and PdM plans.
Ensure compliance with CAT and Meridium recommendations.
Participate in safety committees and implement action plans.
